Package: foodbank
Title: USDA FoodData Central Foundation Foods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Provides the USDA FoodData Central Foundation Foods dataset
    as a set of data frames ready for analysis in R. Includes 436 foods
    with nutrient values, serving size portions, and food categories,
    sourced from the December 2025 release. Data is stored as parquet
    files for efficient access.
